  </section>

  <section class="section bg-gradient-brand text-white">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-white">Ready to transform your GMP Rectification process?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl mb-8 opacity-90">Contact us today to discuss your specific GMP challenges and see how our solution can help</p>
